{"tid":2487990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃榕好鬼黃 ⊙.⊙","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:48:19.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8c985bd44a1251570f486f805655fd5798859ef9","tid":2487990,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"條裙 ⊙.⊙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210413/photo/bkn-20210413220151486-0413_00862_001_03p.jpg?20210413220423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210413220151486-0413_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20210413220423&h=91cccdb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb53a781e827af2899147a119ac1542398339649","tid":2487990,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:27.000Z","msg":"黃榕以斜肩裙現身電影《複製人徐福》首映，她表示喜歡男主角孔劉，大讚對方很Man，並自言喜歡韓仔。問到有否跟韓國男生拍拖？她說：「以前同一個韓仔有過曖昧，但佢唔承認係拍拖，佢係模特兒，嚟香港做嘢，佢成日約我出街，又叫我去佢屋企睇戲，我冇上佢屋企，但有出去飲嘢。我對佢有心動，一直等佢表白，佢會拖我手、搭我膊頭，但就唔表白，唔承認我係女友，最後不了了之，後來佢就返咗去韓國，初時都有喺社交軟件上聯絡，算係霧水情緣。」"},{"pid":"89a9e07d2a1aad037f95502e5f60dfeacbe7a623","tid":2487990,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210413/photo/bkn-20210413220151486-0413_00862_001_02p.jpg?20210413220423\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210413220151486-0413_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20210413220423&h=10e9a890&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adf3735c61a053137318f9e2cabcb6023a8eb9b1","tid":2487990,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"她稱現時單身，坦言已有3年未有拍拖，她無奈地說：「我細個真係好多人追，大個好難戀愛。我依家鍾意大隻仔，鍾意好多肌肉。（有冇叫朋友介紹？）冇，我鍾意自己搵，我鍾意健美比賽嘅男仔，超級大隻嗰啲，覺得好有安全感，雖然我成日參加健美比賽，但都識唔到啱。」"},{"pid":"6b136a8898e27e3155977a9da8895f5fa61389a3","tid":2487990,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adf3735c61a053137318f9e2cabcb6023a8eb9b1","tid":2487990,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"她稱現時單身，坦言已有3年未有拍拖，她無奈地說：「我細個真係好多人追，大個好難戀愛。我依家鍾意大隻仔，鍾意好多肌肉。（有冇叫朋友介紹？）冇，我鍾意自己搵，我鍾意健美比賽嘅男仔，超級大隻嗰啲，覺得好有安全感，雖然我成日參加健美比賽，但都識唔到啱。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"佢之前唔係搵到個有錢男朋友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd22a622f7cd7b1e7ef9e044a59c8ecbbe102bbd","tid":2487990,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"原來都成40碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/unexpected.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceef3f0a89db87b891eacb04b39eac2687314285","tid":2487990,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"嘩 好L核突  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}